event.title: February, 106 existing single-family homes were sold

data.event: Home sales data in Alachua County a mixed bag . In February, 106 existing single-family homes were sold in Alachua and Gilchrist counties.
That’s down 25 percent from the number sold in February 2008, the Florida Association of Realtors announced Monday --- but it’s up from the 73 homes sold in January.
